  </p>

  <h2>Cursor</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://cursor.com/docs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cursor documentation</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://cursor.com/docs/chat" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cursor Chat</a></li>
